        Version 0.3
        -----------
        
        - Added python 3 support
        - Fixxed additional filters
        - Updated documentation
        
        Version 0.2
        -----------
        
        - Added Commandline interface
        - Added method for querying bankruptcies
        - Added tests
        - Added MANIFEST.in
        - Restructured classes
        - Fixed csv output
        - Fixed get_by_kvk() method
        
